# Blog Images Directory

Place blog post hero images and content images here.

## Naming Convention
- Hero images: `post-slug-hero.webp`
- Content images: `post-slug-descriptive-name.webp`

## Requirements
- Format: WebP
- Hero images: 1200x630px
- Content images: 800px max width
- Quality: 80%

